issue.title: 01 Identify what sprint comes next for your class
issue.body:
Go to https://classplanner.codeyourfuture.io/

For your city, work out what the next scheduled class is for the course you're currently taking.

Identify the following:
* Which module is being covered?
* Which sprint is it in the module (note: some modules only have one sprint)?
* How can you find the prep for that sprint?
* How can you find the day-plan?
* What workshop is happening in the day-plan? Is there any preparation you need to do for you?

Every week you should make sure you know what sprint we're covering. You should do the prep, and read the day-plan, before coming to class.

If you need help, ask on Slack.
